Name: Kenbo
About the game: On the warpath again comes a former military man named Kenbo, he swore not to kill again, but some special services again want to recruit him, so Kenbo took up arms and promised to kill anyone who comes to him. Kenbo-Hardcore platformer where the player shoots back from waves of enemies, each wave increases and the player has to make every effort to live to the end, for this he has a machine gun, a pistol and a pack of grenades, can he survive? Game features: - Increasing Complexity - Beautiful Visual style - Dynamic Music
